{"tid":1663201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【勇者鬥惡龍】【戰術post】陣地戰—重整攻勢","createTime":"2019-10-19T09:13:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T10:54:35.000Z","uid":320676,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2138c9c7dda0b273c6fdeef12485ec14a5ae8df2","tid":1663201,"uid":320676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:13:28.000Z","msg":"無可否認，正面對抗我哋難打打贏惡龍，佢哋嘅裝備精良，我哋用棍用鐵通都打唔傷佢<br />\n<br />\n但我哋係贏到㗎喎，以前我哋都贏到，睇下<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PSwZRXSMpf8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPSwZRXSMpf8&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoAbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=013d1416\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PSwZRXSMpf8</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://youtu.be/PSwZRXSMpf8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPSwZRXSMpf8&h=1e78de32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有<span style=\"font-size: large;\">廿隻惡龍</span>，點解會打得贏佢哋？<br />\n<br />\n我覺得係因為：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.氣勢</span><br />\n人人戰意高昂，隨時都準備搵機會，重新包圍政總，佢哋心中有一個<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">明確嘅進攻目標</span></span>，為此，唔怕橡膠彈、布袋彈、催淚煙不惜一切代價進攻<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2.保持合適距離</span><br />\n行埋身係打唔贏龍，只會畀龍㩒喺地下打到爆血。但佢哋亦唔會走到太遠，保持到攻擊距離，可以用遮、磚、垃圾扔死班龍。<br />\n片入面合適距離大概係10-25米左右，手足仲識得<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">上去天橋扔嘢，增強威力。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">3.吹大雞</span><br />\n片中手足睇到有龍捉人後，第一件做嘅事係叫人過嚟圍佢哋，之後亦有手足由石博爬過去號召反包圍，包抄惡龍。<br />\n我哋唯一優勢係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">人數</span>，利用人數，1人1遮，已經可以扔死佢哋。<br />\n因為我哋真係好多人，6個人打1隻龍，咁樣佢有九條命都會死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">4.心態</span><br />\n當時大部分人都用最廢嘅裝，連磚都未用，戴個爛鬼安全帽就上前，但佢哋唔驚，幾百人圍上去扔死惡龍。個陣仲有好多和平新手轉化做勇者一齊扔嘢<br />\n<br />\n而家嘅情況唔同，我哋嘅裝備係進化咗好多，戰力應該提升至係。<br />\n但心態退步咗，有幾千人企喺度等惡龍衝，個個淨係跑走，跟著拉咗幾十個勇者<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7YKSVa8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7YKSVa8.jpg&h=1c2de4ce&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n儘快決定，攻、守、走，10分鐘內要做嘢。如果佢哋仲企定定同惡龍對望又無諗住做嘢(整陷阱都係行動)我建議你快啲行去後排搵地方換衫返屋企<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n⚠️<span style=\"color: red;\">你要確定成條街都係真勇者先可以咁做</span>⚠️<br />\n<br />\n既然惡龍優勢係遠攻用布袋彈橡膠彈，我哋就要拉近距離，橫掂佢都射我哋，我哋要行到去可以攻擊佢嘅距離，15-25米<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記得搶佔高地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n下，咁未行到埋下就畀佢射死？<br />\n<br />\n我都估到你會咁講，所以就揸實你個盾，企上第一排啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3d1xVdE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3d1xVdE.jpg&h=53d6468c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">南亞勇者好型</span><br />\n<br />\n行到過去，就跟著下面啲圖做嘢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T2spMmp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT2spMmp.jpg&h=cbf2d2be&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uhTkjGp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuhTkjGp.jpg&h=f36c7b2b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LTDHx1q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLTDHx1q.jpg&h=14017b35&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kWtsJ75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkWtsJ75.jpg&h=accbd827&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DXd8tzL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDXd8tzL.jpg&h=03c26e0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三角鐵屬性馬係可以撞死佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你哋可以用回收箱當做掩體用，擋到實彈、水炮以外嘅嘢。<br />\n或者係綠色垃圾箱，當做移動掩體<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O0TgCuA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO0TgCuA.png&h=546b086c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁樣打陣地，勇者咪好難走？<br />\n我哋打走/殲滅惡龍，咪唔洗走囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n願榮光歸香港！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">10月20號尖沙嘴見，不分和勇</span>"},{"pid":"3337decf008fc3fc5ea9491c54fbdd1c8c58e0ae","tid":1663201,"uid":172638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:13:38.000Z","msg":"提大家今日有咩活動 10 &middot; 19<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>全日 全民宣傳日</strong></span><br />\n- 宣傳1020民陣大遊行<br />\n[ 各區宣傳，嗌口號，貼文宣，Airdrop ]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>1900 - 2030 國際人道救援祈禱會</strong></span><br />\n- 愛丁堡廣場<br />\n[已獲不反對通知書]"},{"pid":"79dbcbdb8b50ef1fc1e7515a97def5d257d78f35","tid":1663201,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:13:49.000Z","msg":"[創意抗爭] 網民尖沙咀辦「警暴展覽」稱為喚起國際關注<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eotKoS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eotKoS</a><br />\n支持長搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推上國際"},{"pid":"e5ff2c484b4bdd1fd5409b940c08b96545d2fa21","tid":1663201,"uid":172638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:14:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"28e6a4b23452a74ae320bceda15ad9ef8c0f13e9","tid":1663201,"uid":320676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:14:39.000Z","msg":"開錯台，應該係遊戲台先啱"},{"pid":"d6fab3db3bf336b22e0999eb5719fc22914bb00a","tid":1663201,"uid":320676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:15:05.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到"},{"pid":"28a8050f3a70da677188141d79275e57975b5c6d","tid":1663201,"uid":320676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:15:15.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到"},{"pid":"d51d5b27ac33e080cee0143d0175b22e111b2d28","tid":1663201,"uid":320676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:15:25.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到"},{"pid":"a5a57b96cdf35352b449f7fd8e43b3ee176a2ae2","tid":1663201,"uid":320676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:15:38.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到"},{"pid":"e61a008423253349daabb6fbf0b03c2f464eb6dc","tid":1663201,"uid":320676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:15:51.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到"},{"pid":"88f554372656869f93fbbff0903242a17958e8bb","tid":1663201,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:16:29.000Z","msg":"我有預感<br />\n終有一日我地都要打幾次陣地"},{"pid":"847cdf66c36430516d90b0974247a49d9c3e30a8","tid":1663201,"uid":172638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:16:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2244b482444a895b7f472cb88c171dc826832b37","tid":1663201,"uid":172999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:17:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9dfcde446af8589ed8785b9fc4577a2e660b2897","tid":1663201,"uid":172999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88f554372656869f93fbbff0903242a17958e8bb","tid":1663201,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:16:29.000Z","msg":"我有預感<br />\n終有一日我地都要打幾次陣地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:18:42.000Z","msg":"要俾班狗知道香港人係會反抗"},{"pid":"3b97578468106f16aeabbc30dec41b02a9de21c3","tid":1663201,"uid":45914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:20:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a8ea9c0f93abec368876e4e75c1990a2a615ec5","tid":1663201,"uid":320676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b97578468106f16aeabbc30dec41b02a9de21c3","tid":1663201,"uid":45914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:20:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:23:50.000Z","msg":"我淨係講陣地戰可以參考我方法，如果係打遊擊，梗係唔好跟呢個"},{"pid":"4a7718e23d96a21150e33bea96ca40416e3bc036","tid":1663201,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:31:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c088645e325fff445ed1283eaaa3c3a4845a21c4","tid":1663201,"uid":263563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2138c9c7dda0b273c6fdeef12485ec14a5ae8df2","tid":1663201,"uid":320676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:13:28.000Z","msg":"無可否認，正面對抗我哋難打打贏惡龍，佢哋嘅裝備精良，我哋用棍用鐵通都打唔傷佢<br />\n<br />\n但我哋係贏到㗎喎，以前我哋都贏到，睇下<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PSwZRXSMpf8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPSwZRXSMpf8&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoAbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=013d1416\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PSwZRXSMpf8</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://youtu.be/PSwZRXSMpf8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPSwZRXSMpf8&h=1e78de32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有<span style=\"font-size: large;\">廿隻惡龍</span>，點解會打得贏佢哋？<br />\n<br />\n我覺得係因為：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.氣勢</span><br />\n人人戰意高昂，隨時都準備搵機會，重新包圍政總，佢哋心中有一個<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">明確嘅進攻目標</span></span>，為此，唔怕橡膠彈、布袋彈、催淚煙不惜一切代價進攻<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2.保持合適距離</span><br />\n行埋身係打唔贏龍，只會畀龍㩒喺地下打到爆血。但佢哋亦唔會走到太遠，保持到攻擊距離，可以用遮、磚、垃圾扔死班龍。<br />\n片入面合適距離大概係10-25米左右，手足仲識得<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">上去天橋扔嘢，增強威力。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">3.吹大雞</span><br />\n片中手足睇到有龍捉人後，第一件做嘅事係叫人過嚟圍佢哋，之後亦有手足由石博爬過去號召反包圍，包抄惡龍。<br />\n我哋唯一優勢係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">人數</span>，利用人數，1人1遮，已經可以扔死佢哋。<br />\n因為我哋真係好多人，6個人打1隻龍，咁樣佢有九條命都會死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">4.心態</span><br />\n當時大部分人都用最廢嘅裝，連磚都未用，戴個爛鬼安全帽就上前，但佢哋唔驚，幾百人圍上去扔死惡龍。個陣仲有好多和平新手轉化做勇者一齊扔嘢<br />\n<br />\n而家嘅情況唔同，我哋嘅裝備係進化咗好多，戰力應該提升至係。<br />\n但心態退步咗，有幾千人企喺度等惡龍衝，個個淨係跑走，跟著拉咗幾十個勇者<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7YKSVa8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7YKSVa8.jpg&h=1c2de4ce&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n儘快決定，攻、守、走，10分鐘內要做嘢。如果佢哋仲企定定同惡龍對望又無諗住做嘢(整陷阱都係行動)我建議你快啲行去後排搵地方換衫返屋企<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n⚠️<span style=\"color: red;\">你要確定成條街都係真勇者先可以咁做</span>⚠️<br />\n<br />\n既然惡龍優勢係遠攻用布袋彈橡膠彈，我哋就要拉近距離，橫掂佢都射我哋，我哋要行到去可以攻擊佢嘅距離，15-25米<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記得搶佔高地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n下，咁未行到埋下就畀佢射死？<br />\n<br />\n我都估到你會咁講，所以就揸實你個盾，企上第一排啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3d1xVdE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3d1xVdE.jpg&h=53d6468c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">南亞勇者好型</span><br />\n<br />\n行到過去，就跟著下面啲圖做嘢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T2spMmp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT2spMmp.jpg&h=cbf2d2be&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uhTkjGp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuhTkjGp.jpg&h=f36c7b2b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LTDHx1q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLTDHx1q.jpg&h=14017b35&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kWtsJ75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkWtsJ75.jpg&h=accbd827&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DXd8tzL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDXd8tzL.jpg&h=03c26e0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三角鐵屬性馬係可以撞死佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你哋可以用回收箱當做掩體用，擋到實彈、水炮以外嘅嘢。<br />\n或者係綠色垃圾箱，當做移動掩體<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O0TgCuA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO0TgCuA.png&h=546b086c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁樣打陣地，勇者咪好難走？<br />\n我哋打走/殲滅惡龍，咪唔洗走囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n願榮光歸香港！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">10月20號尖沙嘴見，不分和勇</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T10:00:59.000Z","msg":"希望今次大集結可以贏番次"},{"pid":"131defe83c8a70056e75bf05c86287952790001f","tid":1663201,"uid":20298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T10:07:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f6f9bbcbcf891a704821010e8db52093f9d9eac1","tid":1663201,"uid":50848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T10:11:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"34997cf4c95ba61d5906bd1bec062ee187efae75","tid":1663201,"uid":271617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T10:12:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/avzrZ01.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FavzrZ01.gif&h=96fcff81&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9bcfb988839bd903c124cb707c1ba7d830bc870a","tid":1663201,"uid":154557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T10:13:52.000Z","msg":"1020"},{"pid":"c5474c4e61614b401788f6a6c0946a4340ccefbe","tid":1663201,"uid":320676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T10:54:35.000Z","msg":"希望各位勇者可以打贏惡龍，唔好再卡關<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}